{
  "stem": "1042.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anti-Semites-- they were before the war, so that was very good for him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I saw people was hanging, and they were shooting there, so I knew where I came.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I was lucky enough because one of the Jewish police, the officer, was my friend.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to go to school together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he saw me, I just enter, and the police [INAUDIBLE] to him that I am here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I told them in Polish, listen, I beg you, I know for what they called me here, but you're the only one.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Maybe you could do something for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I shall stay alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he says, Joe, I do for you whatever it would be possible.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, this [INAUDIBLE], he turned from there, and he's coming where I was standing by the door.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He is coming, and I had to tell him what happened, that they run away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, so you are the one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he took out the revolver.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When he took out the revolver, my friend, this chief of the police, he says, listen sir, we have-- this is the only mechanic what we have here in garage, and he is the one what we call him always on night when it happens something with your car.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then he turned the revolver on other side, and he give me just a [INAUDIBLE] in my head.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When he turned the revolver-- so the chief of the Jewish police, he told me right away, he will not kill you if you turn his gun this way.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he will stay alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he mentioned to him this is the only one, so he told me, oh, I remember you.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
